- âœ… Clean reruns with idempotent logic
- âœ… Non-interactive execution (e.g. via `curl | bash`)
- âœ… Automatic backup of `/opt/agency_stack` if already present
- âœ… Preparation-only by default (no automatic component install)
- âœ… Optional `--auto-install` flag to trigger full install flow
- âœ… `.installed_ok` marker when prepare phase completes successfully
- âœ… Logs written to `/var/log/agency_stack/install.log`

